Versace, Cavalli May Be Takeover Targets in Coming Months, Corriere Says

-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 
2011-07-07T05:53:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/versace-cavalli-may-be-takeover-targets-in-coming-months-corriere-says.html
Gianni Versace SpA and Roberto
Cavalli SpA are among Italian companies that may be takeover
targets in coming months,  Corriere della Sera  reported, citing a
survey of merger and acquisition experts.  Fondiaria-Sai SpA (FSA) , La Perla and supermarket chain Esselunga
may also be targets, the Italian newspaper’s weekly business
magazine Il Mondo will report tomorrow. Mediobanca SpA and
Labelux are among the possible “predators,” according to
the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  